OL,4,CRiver Trent says 'don't be a hero'
OL,6,FA mother from whose son drowned in the
OL,7,FRiver Trent is backing calls for more
OL,8,Fawareness into preventing drowning.
OL,10,FNicola Jenkins lost her son Owen when
OL,11,Fhe was just 12. He died after going
OL,12,Finto the water at Weir to save two
OL,13,Fgirls.
OL,15,FNicola recalls what happened the day
OL,16,Fthat her son died, saying "He gave me
OL,17,Fa kiss, he told me he loved me and
OL,18,Fthat was the last time I saw him.
