OL,4,CRiver Trent says 'don't be a hero'
OL,6,F"He went in got the first girl who was
OL,7,Fin the most difficulty bought her back
OL,8,Fto the Weir steps, and when he went in
OL,9,Ffor the second girl he went over the
OL,10,Ftop of the hydroplant which is about a
OL,11,F25-metre drop and sadly thats where
OL,12,Fthey found him".
OL,14,FA national warning has now been issued
OL,15,Fabout safety around rivers and lakes
OL,16,Fas we enter June, which saw the most
OL,17,Fwater-related deaths in the UK last
OL,18,Fyear.
