OL,6,F"Unfortunately he leaves us the legacy
OL,7,Fof a little hero and that's the most
OL,8,Fimportant thing to me is to make sure
OL,9,Fother people know what to do in an
OL,10,Femergency.
OL,12,FBryn Coleman, Head of Prevention,
OL,13,FProtection & Fire investigation is
OL,14,Fencouraging others to call, tell and
OL,15,Fthrow if they see someone having
OL,16,Fdifficulty in the water. The advice is:
